# DesignExportStatus

The export status of the job. A newly created job will be `in_progress` and will eventually become `success` or `failed`.

## Enum

* `FAILED` (value: `'failed'`)

* `IN_PROGRESS` (value: `'in_progress'`)

* `SUCCESS` (value: `'success'`)
